01:06:10,642 --> 01:06:11,851
Selamat menikmati.

1107
01:06:13,728 --> 01:06:14,771
Terima kasih, Dokter.

1108
01:06:14,854 --> 01:06:16,147
Kau kembali lagi karena ini?

1109
